.TH "update_xmit_counters" 9 "update_xmit_counters" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
update_xmit_counters \- update PortXmitWait/PortVlXmitWait counters.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" update_xmit_counters
.BI "(struct hfi1_pportdata *ppd "  ","
.BI "u16 link_width "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ppd" 12
info of physical Hfi port
.IP "link_width" 12
new link width after link up or downgrade
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Update the PortXmitWait and PortVlXmitWait counters after
a link up or downgrade event to reflect a link width change.
